  Source:
    Title: Phaedo
    Locus: 100 E
By: Plato
Tags:
  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Uncreate Source of Beauty
---
Nothing makes a thing beautiful but the presence and participation of Beauty in
whatever way or manner obtained. ... By Beauty all beautiful things become
beautiful.
